##estimate mle of rnorm(1d FN)
##numerical method nlm to get mle of FN distribution
f=function(rr,m,s) dnorm(rr,mean=m,sd=s)+dnorm(-rr,mean=m,sd=s)
minusl=function(params,r){
  mu=params[1]
  sigma=params[2]
  -sum(log(f(r,mu,sigma)))
}

